<p><strong>입출력 예시</strong></p>
<blockquote>
  <p>Input-1 <br />
<strong>“3people unFollowed me”</strong> <br />
Output-1 <br />
<strong>“3people Unfollowed Me”</strong></p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>Input-2 <br />
<strong>“for the last week”</strong> <br />
Output-2 <br />
<strong>“For The Last Week”</strong></p>
</blockquote>

